navigate to my 'code' folder
make a new folder (named project)
inside the folder create a file called 'index.js'
open terminal and navigate to the proect folder
run command "npm init -y"
run command "npm install express"
open index.js
require xpress at the top of the file 
initialize the app object/variable

Create the home page route
    call app.get()
    set'/' as the path (first arg)
    write callback function with req,res
    call res.send('hello world')

call app.listen(3001) to keep server open